Image 1: shade flat
Image 2: shade smooth
Image 3: shade flat with modifier
Image 4: shade smooth with modifier
The shade smooth made the polygonal mesh that the sphere is made of much less noticeable than the shade flat.
The same with the modifier, but the shade flat with modifier had much smaller polygons, though they were still noticeable.

Image 5: 250W light power 
Image 6: light moved closer half the distance
Image 7: disk area light

images 5 and 6 show us that the irradiance depends on the position and power of lighting because the closer and more powerful the lighting is,
the brighter the scene will be
